title: Saturday Night Live Season 16 Complete
description:
SNL Season 16 (1990-1991)

The 16th Season Of Saturday Night Live Gets A Whole Lot Better And Plus A Fresh New Batch Of Cast Members.

CHRIS FARLEY,ROB SCHINDER,ADAM SANDLER,CHRIS ROCK,TIM MEADOWS AND THE OTHERS ALL MAKE THEIR DEBUTS IN THE 16th SEASON.

AND PLUS THIS WAS DENNIS MILLER'S LAST SEASON DOING THE WEEKEND UPDATE.

AND PLUS IT HAS PATRICK SWAYZE AND CHRIS FARLEY DOING THE CHIPPENDALES SKETCH ON THE OCTOBER 27th 1990 SHOW.

SO HERE IS SEASON 16.
